tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE QuantumDataPackets (
    packet_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    source_node VARCHAR(255),
    destination_node VARCHAR(255),
    packet_size INT,
    routing_algorithm VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE QuantumConnections (
    connection_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    node1_id INT,
    node2_id INT,
    connection_type VARCHAR(50),
    FOREIGN KEY (node1_id) REFERENCES QuantumNodes(node_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (node2_id) REFERENCES QuantumNodes(node_id)
);

CREATE TABLE QuantumPackets (
    packet_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    packet_size INT,
    source_node_id INT,
    destination_node_id INT,
    received BOOLEAN,
    FOREIGN KEY (source_node_id) REFERENCES QuantumNodes(node_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (destination_node_id) REFERENCES QuantumNodes(node_id)
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_packets (
    packet_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    source_address VARCHAR(255),
    destination_address VARCHAR(255),
    packet_size INT,
    creation_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE quantum_routing_nodes (
    node_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    node_name VARCHAR(255),
    node_location VARCHAR(255),
    node_status VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE quantum_links (
    link_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    source_node_id INT,
    destination_node_id INT,
    link_speed INT,
    link_capacity INT
)

CREATE TABLE quantum_routing_logs (
    log_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    packet_id INT,
    source_node_id INT,
    destination_node_id INT,
    route_calculated_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE quantum_packets (
  packet_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  packet_size INT NOT NULL,
  source_device INT NOT NULL,
  destination_device INT NOT NULL,
  arrival_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_routing (
  route_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  source_device INT NOT NULL,
  destination_device INT NOT NULL,
  route_path VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  hop_count INT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_performance (
  performance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  link_id INT NOT NULL,
  transmitted_packets INT NOT NULL,
  successful_packets INT NOT NULL,
  transmission_rate DECIMAL(5, 2) NOT NULL
);
